body:
This mod is, easy way to fix rare crash with Particle of Dynamic Trees.


```
Mod fixes this crash:
java.lang.NullPointerException: Cannot invoke "net.minecraft.client.particle.Particle.m_107253_(float, float, float)" because "particle" is null
	at com.ferreusveritas.dynamictrees.init.DTClient.addDustParticle(DTClient.java:212) ~[DynamicTrees-1.20.1-1.4.7.jar%23363!/:1.20.1-1.4.7] {re:classloading}
	at com.ferreusveritas.dynamictrees.init.DTClient.crushLeavesBlock(DTClient.java:259) ~[DynamicTrees-1.20.1-1.4.7.jar%23363!/:1.20.1-1.4.7] {re:classloading}
	at com.ferreusveritas.dynamictrees.block.leaves.DynamicLeavesBlock.m_142072_(DynamicLeavesBlock.java:644) ~[DynamicTrees-1.20.1-1.4.7.jar%23363!/:1.20.1-1.4.7] {re:classloading}
```



**This mod was created with the support of Minecraft hosting minely.net**
